description:
Will automatically set dynamic row height
based on the material table element parent (head, body, etc).
propChildren: Should be valid <tr> children such as `TableCell`.
propClasses: Override or extend the styles applied to the component.
propComponent:
The component used for the root node.
Either a string to use a HTML element or a component.
propHover: If `true`, the table row will shade on hover.
propSelected: If `true`, the table row will have the selected shading.
stylesRoot: Styles applied to the root element.
stylesSelected: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if `selected={true}`.
stylesHover: Pseudo-class applied to the root element if `hover={true}`.
stylesHead: Styles applied to the root element if table variant="head".
stylesFooter: Styles applied to the root element if table variant="footer".
